{"tid":762184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇泰仔泰女可以幫我尋親？","createTime":"2018-07-31T05:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T06:32:43.000Z","uid":5703,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a38373f14d8787c9f16d5d0cd3e6eefc495c236b","tid":762184,"uid":5703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:22:44.000Z","msg":"話說我屋企一行十人會係下星期五去泰國尋親<br />\n今次遠赴泰國主要係搵爺爺嘅呀哥(已去世)嘅十個仔女<br />\n事源係爺哥同佢老婆係鄉下過左身<br />\n骨灰放左係鄉下<br />\n我個仆街呀叔話拜爺哥會影響風水<br />\n所以下令啲子孫唔可以拜祭爺哥<br />\n仲收埋左爺哥既墓張相<br />\n爸爸想搵爺哥個十個仔女睇下佢地會唔會想帶爺哥既骨灰去泰國<br />\n但我爸爸已經40年冇返過泰國<br />\n得返幾張舊相同舊卡片<br />\n有冇巴絲可以幫下我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a8290716735e361df6323155ecf441eae6124c","tid":762184,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"痴線"},{"pid":"aa0a9d2a210953dd8a53f5a0d4a143ad46ebc5e6","tid":762184,"uid":169116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"泰北孤軍後人?"},{"pid":"061bd4aef5c1379d69e36b4b6af9648c71c224c7","tid":762184,"uid":5703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:49:53.000Z","msg":"整返張人物關係圖先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/133851_8f203d6ebb0c4c3b06346627a2f72276.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F133851_8f203d6ebb0c4c3b06346627a2f72276.png&h=3f21dca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n線索1:爺爺哥哥十個仔女其中兩個仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/134247_45c12a84c57603e5c244927294d8bab6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F134247_45c12a84c57603e5c244927294d8bab6.png&h=ac521f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n線索2: 爺爺哥哥十個仔女其中一個女<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/134405_9bec1673580d1db9ba8a7b9a4f09d2c9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F134405_9bec1673580d1db9ba8a7b9a4f09d2c9.png&h=017707f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n線索3:爺爺有錢弟弟三個仔(3個細路)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/134555_f8d681c41ce8740a001e4e4d45f10029.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F134555_f8d681c41ce8740a001e4e4d45f10029.png&h=6d8f1954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n線索4:爺爺有錢弟弟個女婿卡片<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/134645_65e43f9b9a1a5c36a16261d78ee3ab8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F134645_65e43f9b9a1a5c36a16261d78ee3ab8a.png&h=98eda54f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n線索5:爺爺契弟老婆卡片<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/134754_5b21d20a061a36f6d7ffb064acfe2668.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F134754_5b21d20a061a36f6d7ffb064acfe2668.png&h=76a6260d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/134755_80d83e8f4a661a027190c0f7435572fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F134755_80d83e8f4a661a027190c0f7435572fb.png&h=90f98ec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n線索6:爺爺哥哥舊地址<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/134858_18e34fc901689e5df574f8dfaa6152f1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F134858_18e34fc901689e5df574f8dfaa6152f1.png&h=89cdf638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n線索7:爺爺弟弟舊地址<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/134949_0c7bd3d3c283f9ecc45aef0082dbc512.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F134949_0c7bd3d3c283f9ecc45aef0082dbc512.png&h=bcf